### Create a new user group (Requires Admin or Teacher)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/user-groups
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "name": "Nowa Grupa Testowa",
  "description": "Opis grupy"
}

### Get all groups (Requires Admin or Teacher)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/user-groups
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Get specific group (Requires Admin or GroupOwner)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/user-groups/1
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Update group (Requires Admin or GroupOwner)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/user-groups/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "name": "Zmieniona Nazwa",
  "description": "Zmieniony opis"
}

### Add student to group (Requires Admin or GroupOwner)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/user-groups/1/members/2
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Remove student from group (Requires Admin or GroupOwner)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/user-groups/1/members/2
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Delete group (Requires Admin or GroupOwner)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/user-groups/1
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
